<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.13">
<l>vaṇṭamar pūṅkuḻa lāycci makaṉākak</l>
<l>koṇṭu vaḷarkkiṉṟa kōvalak kuṭṭaṟku</l>
<l>vaṇṭamu nāṭu maṭaṅka viḻuṅkiya</l>
<l>kaṇṭa miruntavā kāṇīrē kārikai yīrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ladies, see the quality of the throat that swallowed heaven and earth whole,</l>
<l>of the cowherd boy who was taken in and is being raised</l>
<l>as the son of the cowherdess whose curly hair</l>
<l>[is adorned with] flowers where bees abide. Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
